Absolutely stunning home in Bridges on Lake Houston! If you are looking for a 2700+ square foot 1 story home with FIVE bedrooms on a HUGE homesite just steps from Lake Houston, then look no further! Lovely brick and stone elevation with nicely appointed landscaping package! Long foyer with private wing containing 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths! This home has a THREE car TANDEM garage! If you need boat storage, this one is plenty large enough to hold it! Oversized utility room with lots of space for extra storage! This is one of the largest kitchen/dining/family rooms I have seen in a home of this size! PLUS another bonus room off the kitchen - so many possibilities! Private master suite with enormous walk in closet! Exit the home onto the back patio and gawk at this yard! Unreal! All this while enjoying the wonderful lake breeze. Make this home in Bridges your everyday staycation! You will be so glad you did!
